{"tid":720670,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(又有得笑) 國產劇女主角竟是神奇女俠  導演稱靈感來自漫威大片","createTime":"2018-06-28T05:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T06:13:27.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3c0bd73cb3109fbab9922f24f0d61a087cd6ba","tid":720670,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:50:33.000Z","msg":"2018年暑期檔奇幻浪漫愛情喜劇《精靈的後裔》將於7月11日登陸優酷視頻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180627_gtz_412_8/gamersky_03small_06_2018627195661D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180627_gtz_412_8%2Fgamersky_03small_06_2018627195661D.jpg&h=d93f86fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片《精靈的後裔》由導演一然傾力執導，由青年演員王嵛與伍麟凱領銜主演。<br />\n<br />\n　　影片講述了項大麗（王嵛飾）夢想做一名警察行俠仗義，為了實現她的終極願望卻只能從一名保安做起。在一次執行任務當中，她意外獲得&ldquo;天外神力&rdquo;成為了一位&ldquo;精靈的後裔&rdquo;，而一名自稱&ldquo;關羽後人&rdquo;的&ldquo;精靈護衛&rdquo;成為了她的貼身護花使者，暗中幫她&ldquo;法力無邊，神通廣大&rdquo;。項大麗在接下來的一次重要任務中臨危受命與搭檔&ldquo;覓踪大神&rdquo;華聲（鄧皓飾）聯手尋找一名重要人物&ldquo;神秘豪二代&rdquo;（伍麟凱飾），不料與大反派&ldquo;黑衣人&rdquo;遭遇戰鬥，一段啼笑皆非的傳奇故事就此上演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180627_gtz_412_8/gamersky_02small_04_2018627195611D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180627_gtz_412_8%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2018627195611D.jpg&h=d892a6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片的導演一然說道：&ldquo;影片創作的靈感最初就來自《神奇女俠》，雖然原本是個好萊塢漫威奇幻大片，人物都是脫離真實生活的，但相信很多女孩都希望成為劇中人，我想把人物更接地氣，變為小人物的勵志故事，再普通的人也會有夢想，都有奮鬥的權利，夢想面前人人平等！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/upimg/pic/2018/06/27/small_201806272044281138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fupimg%2Fpic%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2Fsmall_201806272044281138.jpg&h=db1ce48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更多劇照：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180627_gtz_412_8/gamersky_01small_02_20186271956B99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180627_gtz_412_8%2Fgamersky_01small_02_20186271956B99.jpg&h=b783f576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180627_gtz_412_8/gamersky_04small_08_20186271956D0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180627_gtz_412_8%2Fgamersky_04small_08_20186271956D0E.jpg&h=35966cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180627_gtz_412_8/gamersky_06small_12_2018627195697C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180627_gtz_412_8%2Fgamersky_06small_12_2018627195697C.jpg&h=e5ea22c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/28/134908_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F28%2F134908_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=56f61bf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06838e873a8c72c43f2a6c5108c0912348168a46","tid":720670,"uid":72730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ee663d5d7c89f40999c03c104d98ab0b540280","tid":720670,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"個導演算係漫威粉定DC粉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68c0f686f96884980632fb937abec266ee13aeb","tid":720670,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0820cbfef40723563d02c477ed6d748e922f7404","tid":720670,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T05:5